FBIS4-18200 "drweu063__a94007" FBIS-WEU-94-063-A Daily Report 1 April 1994 ANNEX Inter-European Affairs Council To Finance EBRD's Nuclear Safety Account Council To Finance EBRD's Nuclear Safety Account BR0104102994 Brussels Textline Database in English 31 Mar 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY BR0104102994 Brussels Textline Database English BFN [Unattributed article: "Council Decides Contribution To EBRD Nuclear Safety Account"; as released by EUROPE] [Text] The Council of the European Union has adopted the decision on conclusion of the agreement (in the form of an exchange of letters) negotiated by the European Commission concerning the Community contribution of ECU20 million to the EBRD's (European Bank for Reconstruction and Development) nuclear safety account. The money is to be used to improve the safety of nuclear power stations in Central and East European countries and the republics of the ex-USSR.
